  "text": "Pathway-based approaches for analyzing gene expression data have become increasingly popular in recent years. Most methods have approached the problem from a multiple hypotheses testing perspective. However, the latent group lasso approach proposed by Jacob et al. [CITATION_1] allows the incorporation of pathway information into regression models as well.",
